### ğŸ“¦ Installation

Install the package from PyPI:

```sh
pip install selfrevolve
```

Run the API and UI:

```sh
revolve-api
```

For local development instructions, see [contributor-README.md](https://huggingface.co/kramster/evolve-mistral).

